column2: SELECT ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY g) #, p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, ( (p.g + #* (p.g - p.r) + #) ) as B, p.fracDev_g, p.petroRad_g as PRadius, p.petroR9#_g as PRadius9#, p.expAB_g as ratioba, p.expRad_g as efscale, p.deVRad_g as vfscale, s.z as redshift, ( (p.g + #* (p.g - p.r) + #) + (#*LOG1# (#*PI () * (p.petroR9#_g) * (p.petroR9#_g) )) + (#*LOG1# (p.expAB_g) ) - (#*LOG1# (#+s.z) )) as moB, (s.z* (#/#) ) as Distancepc, ( (p.g + #* (p.g - p.r) + #) - #* (LOG1# ((s.z* (#/#) )) )) as MB, ( (p.petroR9#_g) * (#) ) as PRadius9#radian, ( (p.petroR9#_g) * (#) * (s.z* (#/#) )) as PRadius9#pc, ( (p.expRad_g) * (#) ) as efscaleradian, ( (p.expRad_g) * (#) * (s.z* (#/#) )) as efscalepc, s.subClass, s.elodieFeH as metallicity_spec, st.ssfr_mean as sSFR, st.logMass as msg, st.metallicity as metallicity_meth, e.bpt, e.Flux_Ha_#, e.Flux_NI_#, e.Flux_NII_#, e.Flux_OII_#, e.Flux_OIII_#, replace (dbo.fGetUrlNavId (p.objID) , #, #) as link, dbo.fPhotoFlagsN (flags) as flags FROM photoObj p JOIN specObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust st ON st.specObjID = s.specObjID JOIN emissionLinesPort e ON e.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE p.type = # AND p.r < = # AND p.fracDev_g < = # AND p.expAB_g > # AND s.z BETWEEN # AND # AND s.zWarning = # AND ( (p.g + #* (p.g - p.r) + #) + (#*LOG1# (#*#* (p.petroR9#_g) * (p.petroR9#_g) )) + (#*LOG1# (p.expAB_g) ) - (#*LOG1# (#+s.z) )) BETWEEN # AND # AND st.ssfr_mean > # ORDER BY p.g, #
